text: Rottenburg an der Laaber is a town in Landshut, in Bavaria, Germany. It is on the river Große Laber, 21 km northwest of Landshut. ==Notable residents== *Max Ritter von Müller (1887-1918), World War I fighter ace and highest scoring Bavarian in the war ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Landshut (district)
title: Rottenburg an der Laaber
